<emphasis id="B979E372DC66FFE2F6DD362AFD6BF9DB" bold="true" box="[740,763,1604,1624]" pageId="11" pageNumber="788">36</emphasis>
) male pronotum, elytra, and abdominal segment III (holotype); (
<emphasis id="B979E372DC66FFE2F5E83635FE78F9EC" bold="true" box="[465,488,1627,1647]" pageId="11" pageNumber="788">37</emphasis>
) head in lateral view; (
<emphasis id="B979E372DC66FFE2F6F23635FC90F9EC" bold="true" box="[715,768,1627,1647]" pageId="11" pageNumber="788">38-39</emphasis>
) median lobe of aedeagus in lateral and in ventral view; (
<emphasis id="B979E372DC66FFE2F5A7361CFE25F905" bold="true" box="[414,437,1650,1670]" pageId="11" pageNumber="788">40</emphasis>
) apical lobe of paramere; (
<emphasis id="B979E372DC66FFE2F682361CFD42F905" bold="true" box="[699,722,1650,1670]" pageId="11" pageNumber="788">41</emphasis>
) female sternite VIII; (
<emphasis id="B979E372DC66FFE2F78A361CFC5AF905" bold="true" box="[947,970,1650,1670]" pageId="11" pageNumber="788">42</emphasis>
